[2]: http://assistance.orange.fr/l-application-livephone-sur-pc-4898.php
[3]: https://bitbucket.org/xtab/siproxd_orange/wiki/Home
[4]: https://bitbucket.org/xtab/siproxd_orange/wiki/Home
